    "description": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>欢迎来到 VIA </strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >踏入一个充满战略性 PvP 战斗的中世纪奇幻世界，无需繁琐的升级。在 VIA 中，你可以选择成为商人、守卫或盗贼——成功取决于你的装备、决策和技能！</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>核心特点：</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3271330/extras/b37f0a94737ca3c6a466983d1755d3ac.avif?t=1731253225\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3271330/extras_big/b37f0a94737ca3c6a466983d1755d3ac.avif?t=1731253225 width=800 height=186 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >在激烈的实时战斗中展示你的战斗技巧，这里反应速度和战术与角色的力量同样重要。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3271330/extras/ae973457d4a610404a24e99c829ea1fa.poster.avif?t=1731253225\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3271330/extras/ae973457d4a610404a24e99c829ea1fa.webm?t=1731253225\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3271330/extras/ae973457d4a610404a24e99c829ea1fa.mp4?t=1731253225\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3271330/extras/562111db92dff7c255a3be0b860865f6.avif?t=1731253225\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3271330/extras_big/562111db92dff7c255a3be0b860865f6.avif?t=1731253225 width=800 height=186 /></span></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>骑士</strong><br>挥舞巨大的双手剑，以无与伦比的防御能力主宰近战战场。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3271330/extras/ac72002bd7e4a73bf4ba8334f43c1a51.poster.avif?t=1731253225\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3271330/extras/ac72002bd7e4a73bf4ba8334f43c1a51.webm?t=1731253225\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3271330/extras/ac72002bd7e4a73bf4ba8334f43c1a51.mp4?t=1731253225\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>法师</strong><br>操控奥术力量，释放毁灭性的范围法术和魔法护盾。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3271330/extras/916dd556fae041d19e2e1265812e164a.poster.avif?t=1731253225\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3271330/extras/916dd556fae041d19e2e1265812e164a.webm?t=1731253225\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3271330/extras/916dd556fae041d19e2e1265812e164a.mp4?t=1731253225\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>弓箭手</strong><br>利用精准打击和自然之力，从远距离消灭敌人。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3271330/extras/6b043cb1e756004ebb49f156ea163773.avif?t=1731253225\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3271330/extras_big/6b043cb1e756004ebb49f156ea163773.avif?t=1731253225 width=800 height=450 /></span></p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3271330/extras/690849c1d02f1eb607c7292c631d7a73.avif?t=1731253225\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3271330/extras_big/690849c1d02f1eb607c7292c631d7a73.avif?t=1731253225 width=800 height=186 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >VIA 的核心是商队系统，商人们在城镇之间运送贵重货物。盗贼则潜伏伺机抢夺，而守卫负责保护商队。这一平衡的系统提供了高风险的 PvP 战斗，策略和风险管理至关重要。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3271330/extras/d1694680e4f668ff0b17adb110ae97c5.poster.avif?t=1731253225\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3271330/extras/d1694680e4f668ff0b17adb110ae97c5.webm?t=1731253225\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3271330/extras/d1694680e4f668ff0b17adb110ae97c5.mp4?t=1731253225\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3271330/extras/d2d522f1d6669323f16afe32df57ba87.avif?t=1731253225\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3271330/extras_big/d2d522f1d6669323f16afe32df57ba87.avif?t=1731253225 width=800 height=186 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >在开放世界中收集资源，猎杀稀有怪物，并打造强力装备，助你在战斗中立于不败之地。丰富的制作系统让你在成长中感受到实力的提升。告别无尽的升级，专注于提升装备和职业技能，增强你的力量和影响力。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3271330/extras/2c0eeed1a181332b98113b6726f86e57.avif?t=1731253225\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3271330/extras_big/2c0eeed1a181332b98113b6726f86e57.avif?t=1731253225 width=800 height=186 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >与传奇怪物展开史诗般的对决，探索广阔的开放世界，在危险的地牢中发现隐藏的宝藏。你可以单人游戏或与好友组队，挑战团队副本或进行激烈的 PvP 战斗。</p>",
